OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1775661069
OL,3,CThree charged with murder over
OL,4,CBarnsley pedestrian death
OL,6,FOn Monday 6 April 60-year-old Mark
OL,7,FWigley, 38-year-old Sarah Louise
OL,8,FWigley and 53-year-old Neil Shaw, all
OL,9,Fof Royston Road, Barnsley were charged
OL,10,Fwith murder.
OL,12,FAll three have been remanded in
OL,13,Fcustody and are due to appear before
OL,14,FSheffield Magistrates' Court on 7
OL,15,FApril.
OL,17,FSouth Yorkshire Police say a 33-year-
OL,18,Fold man and a 17-year-old boy arrested
OL,19,Fon Saturday (4 April) on suspicion of
OL,20,Fmurder both remain on bail.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
